{"id": 126, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在办公室的时候你在讨厌什么？", "description": "很多公司都采用了开放式办公布局，方便员工之间沟通，但过度的开放式空间，很多人因为无法集中注意力或被打扰而无法专心工作。啊嗷，你是不是也一样悲桑！\r\n", "record_count": 1877, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194339ms2unhfvZjSV3JPW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-10-31T08:24:55Z", "questions": [{"id": 114, "title": "你在办公室的时候你在讨厌什么？", "content": "你在办公室的时候你在讨厌什么？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 972, "content": "不想我买的东西啊我家人的照片啊什么的被人看到", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192530g9pvubPZyofhwKA3.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 973, "content": "办公室吵死了，我啥也干不了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193113kDlvQAF4n1w8XPmK.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 974, "content": "不想工作一会儿就被别人打断聊天或者突然派活儿", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192531yuSR61oFO8WdMKpj.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 975, "content": "讨厌我难得认真工作的思绪被QQ和微信打断", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192531BqUvLaH7nipzurmD.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 976, "content": "很烦没有合适的地方私下聊天或者打电话", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192531UK64WukljR91qExo.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 977, "content": "环顾四周都没个让人能放松身心的地方", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192531IAFqmNhnR1JY4vxS.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}